      "id": "0ce66f2f-e8e6-49ba-9cb2-8879f64e2984",
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "text": "Dr. Sreedath is an exceptional teacher who truly stands out in the AI learning space. His ability to break down complex concepts and build them from first principles makes the learning experience incredibly accessible—even for those with no prior exposure. The way he explained context engineering was particularly powerful. He demystified how to effectively work within the finite context window of LLMs, showing how to structure and prioritize context elements to drive efficient and accurate responses. This is not just useful—it’s a foundational skill for anyone serious about working in AI. The course itself was brilliantly designed—highly intuitive, deeply practical, and hands-on. Rather than just theory, we actively explored how different context elements influence LLM behavior, and saw firsthand how small changes can significantly impact outputs. One of the standout aspects was the end-of-session quizzes, which reinforced learning and ensured we truly internalized the concepts. The three capstone projects, led by all three founders, were equally impressive—each offering a unique perspective on real-world AI software development and giving us the chance to apply what we learned in meaningful ways. Doubt-clearing sessions were handled with great clarity and patience, making the entire experience even more enriching. And perhaps the most incredible part—this level of high-quality, “gold-standard” content is offered for free. That’s truly commendable. I’m genuinely grateful to Dr. Sreedath and the entire Vizuara team for empowering learners to transition into AI with such thoughtfully crafted programs. Thank you, Vizuara—you absolutely rock!",
