      "text": "I attended the Modern Software Engineering course at Vizuara, taught by Dr. Raj sir, and it was a wonderful learning experience. He is an excellent teacher who truly understands current industry needs and what professionals must do to upskill in today’s AI-driven market. Through this course, I learned how to develop projects end-to-end using Claude Code and how to productize them by applying security hardening, testing pyramids, CI/CD workflows, and cloud deployment. The course covered the entire software development lifecycle, with iterative development using different AI tools available in the market. This practical, real-world approach made the learning extremely valuable. The course is very well structured. Dr. Raj sir explains every concept clearly first and then guides us through hands-on practical sessions during the class itself. This teaching style helped me understand the concepts deeply and gain confidence in applying them. The daily hands-on projects further reinforced what was taught in each session and made me comfortable using the concepts on my own. He also maintained class timings very well, which made it easier to plan my workday even though the sessions were conducted on weekdays. Every concept taught was immediately demonstrated in practice, and everything was explained from scratch, so no prior experience was required. This approach can also be seen in his Build LLM from Scratch lectures on YouTube. Despite graduating from MIT, Dr. Raj sir chose to stay in India and serve the Indian community by teaching AI courses during this challenging transition period. This is truly a great service to the nation. Thank you, Dr. Raj sir and Vizuara, for teaching me AI concepts and making me confident to transition into AI-driven software development.",
