      "text": "I am a senior software professional with extensive experience in the IT industry. I was introduced to Vizuara AI courses last year, and the learning journey since then has been extremely rewarding. I can confidently say that the “Transformers for Vision” bootcamp is one of the best programs I have attended. The curriculum was comprehensive and covered concepts in great depth, which significantly strengthened my understanding of modern computer vision models and architectures. I am especially grateful to the trainer, Dr. Sreedath Panat, for his exceptional teaching style. He put in extraordinary effort to ensure every concept was clearly explained, often going beyond the planned syllabus and adding additional sessions to provide completeness and clarity. His passion for teaching and attention to detail truly set this program apart. Overall, this bootcamp was absolutely worth the investment, and I look forward to enrolling in future programs conducted by Dr. Panat.",
