      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "text": "This course was great! I learned so much about Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning,it was really easy to follow. Really enjoyed Vizuara Foundation of AI Model Course. The instructor explained things clearly, and I feel much more confident now. Thanks to this course, I now have a solid foundation in machine learning, deep learning, and data science, and I feel well-equipped to pursue exciting opportunities in the AI field. I highly recommend this AI course to anyone who is serious about understanding and working with artificial intelligence, whether you're a beginner or looking to upskill.",
